originalText.text: I gotta say, Ive stumbled upon one of the best smoke shops ever!! Located in the heart of LES, good people, good vibes and top quality products. It doesnt get better than this, definitely left here a happy customer and will definitely return!!!!

originalText.text: On here it shows the store has confirmed the schedule 2 weeks ago. But today I stood outside in the heat for an hour and the store remained closed. From 1230 PM to 130 PM. After traveling 11 miles wasting my day off and gas this is not how you play with customers time. It’s not difficult to update the consumer via your IG Story if there is a change of schedule

originalText.text: This is top tier cannibus for the connoisseur. Exceptional hard to find strains that you will thoroughly enjoy. They have Zheetos, the best strain I’ve ever had. It will take you from a bad mood to great, tired to awake, stressed to zen. Can you put a price on happiness?…yes and the ish is expensive but worth it. Treat yourself. Amazing high quality selection, friendly and knowledgeable…and they sell the best fkn stickers in NYC
